<paragraph id="8BB936A3A4661877FF36FE41D2D1FDF9" blockId="2.[151,1436,437,823]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
The nominal genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D20A4661877FEDFFE41D413FE28" box="[382,561,437,462]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Porphyrochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B972EAB1A4661877FEDFFE41D413FE28" box="[382,561,437,462]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Porphyrochroa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has generally been overlooked since it was described by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF974B52A4661877FB6EFE41D3BAFE29" author="Melander" box="[1231,1432,437,463]" pageId="2" pageNumber="39" refString="Melander, A. L. (1928) Diptera, Fam. Empididae. Genera Insectorum, 185 [1927], 1 - 434." type="journal article" year="1928">
Melander (
<number id="3DCE2484A4661877FAEEFE41D3ADFE29" box="[1359,1423,437,463]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" value="1928.0">1928</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EF974B52A4661877FF36FE29D715FE11" author="Smith" box="[151,311,477,503]" pageId="2" pageNumber="39" refString="Smith, K. G. V. (1967) Family Empididae (Empidae, Hybotidae). In: A Catalogue of the Diptera of the Americas south of the United States. Sao Paulo, Departamento de Zoologia, 67 pp." type="book" year="1967">
Smith (
<number id="3DCE2484A4661877FF50FE29D70CFE11" box="[241,302,477,503]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" value="1967.0">1967</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
considered it a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D20A4661877FD4EFE29D5AFFE10" box="[751,909,477,502]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Macrostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B972EAB1A4661877FD4EFE29D5AFFE10" box="[751,909,477,502]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Macrostomus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D20A4661877FC00FE29D276FE10" box="[929,1108,477,502]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Porphyrochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B972EAB1A4661877FC00FE29D276FE10" box="[929,1108,477,502]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Porphyrochroa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was finally revalidated by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF974B52A4661877FF36FDF1D71EFDF9" author="Rafael" box="[151,316,517,543]" pageId="2" pageNumber="39" refString="Rafael, J. A. (2001) Redescricao de duas especies neotropicais de Empididae (Diptera) descritas por Curran e revalidacao do genero Prophyrochroa. Iheringia, Serie Zoologia, 90, 127 - 132." type="journal article" year="2001">
Rafael (
<number id="3DCE2484A4661877FF52FDF1D711FDF9" box="[243,307,517,543]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" value="2001.0">2001</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. In this paper, Rafael also transferred 
<taxonomicName id="4C064D20A4661877FD59FDF1D275FDF9" authority="Curran" authorityName="Curran" box="[760,1111,517,543]" class="Insecta" family="Empididae" genus="Axelempis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciventris">
<emphasis id="B972EAB1A4661877FD59FDF1D5DCFDF8" box="[760,1022,517,542]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Axelempis fasciventris</emphasis>
Curran
</taxonomicName>
to the genus.
</paragraph>
